column7: can register for the Inflatable 5k Run at www.inflatable5k.com. On the homepage there is a link to the registration page where you can create an account and sign up for the race.

Duh-duh-duh-duh is usually used to represent a single four count beat in music. This beat can be used for timing various musical pieces or for counting sequences when playing instruments. It can also be used to add a suspenseful or dramatic effect in film or television.
